id: 26
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I found the usable brand anchors: white primary/submark logos, square-button navigation, dark/bright section themes, poetic copy, 7-day 11am-late dining, Star Brisbane address, phone, SevenRooms booking, gift voucher links, functions, banquets, drinks, and the menu price anchors that were visible."}

